        "Description": "Good evening, 47.\n\nHokkaido has become the source of an unusual outbreak—five individuals now stand at the center of containment. Two security guards must be removed beneath falling objects, their deaths dismissed as unfortunate accidents. Another guard is to meet a different accidental end, triggered by a device prepared in advance. All three operations must be carried out while maintaining the appearance of a suited guest.\n\nThe remaining two targets—a guest and the yoga instructor—require a quieter finish. Both are to be eliminated by drowning, while disguised as the facility’s repair staff.\n\nDistance and preparation will be your greatest allies. Four of these deaths should look like fate, not design.\n\nLet the snow bury the truth.",
